Subject: Re: [T2] alloy wheels

Turn the steering wheel all the way to the right. Look under the drivers side
from behind the wheel. You will see the speedo cable going into the center
between the two tubes. Grab the cable and try to pull it out, gently!! If it
comes out, the end is not connected.


